OL,3,CGunman 'kills six of his relatives and
OL,4,Cthen himself' in Iowa domestic dispute
OL,6,FA man is suspected of killing six
OL,7,Ffamily members after a domestic
OL,8,Fdispute, before shooting himself in
OL,9,FIowa.
OL,11,FThe alleged gunman reportedly took his
OL,12,Flife when confronted by police just
OL,13,Fafter noon on Monday.
OL,15,FUS police discovered four bodies at a
OL,16,Fhouse in Muscatine and later found
OL,17,Fsuspect Ryan Willis McFarland, 52,
OL,18,Fwith a self-inflicted gunshot wound on
OL,19,Fa riverfront trail near a pedestrian
OL,20,Fbridge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
