OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780481194
OL,3,CGunman 'kills six of his relatives and
OL,4,Cthen himself' in Iowa domestic dispute
OL,6,FLocal police chief Anthony Kies called
OL,7,Fthe massacre an "act of evil".
OL,9,FDetectives later discovered two other
OL,10,Fmen dead from apparent gunshot wounds
OL,11,Felsewhere in the city.
OL,13,FOne man was in his home, and the other
OL,14,Fwas pronounced dead inside a business
OL,15,Fpremises.
OL,17,FDuring a news conference, Kies said
OL,18,Fthe latest US mass shooting victims
OL,19,Fare believed to be McFarland's
OL,20,Frelatives.
