OL,3,CGunman 'kills six of his relatives and
OL,4,Cthen himself' in Iowa domestic dispute
OL,6,F"Today I simply do not have the
OL,7,Fwords," Kies said. "This act of evil
OL,8,Fand what it has done to our community.
OL,10,F"While talking to Ryan Willis
OL,11,FMcFarland, he took his own life."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FLaw enforcement has yet to release the
OL,19,Fnames of the victims and any details
OL,20,Fabout them.
