OL,3,CGunman 'kills six of his relatives and
OL,4,Cthen himself' in Iowa domestic dispute
OL,6,FKies confirmed that McFarland had a
OL,7,Fcriminal record, but did not share
OL,8,Ffurther details.
OL,10,FMuscatine sits on the Mississippi
OL,11,FRiver and has a population of
OL,12,Fapproximately 23,500.
